item.title: CVE-2023-4151|2024-08-02T07:17:12.138Z -- unknown -- store%20locator%20wordpress
item.description: The Store Locator WordPress plugin before 1.4.13 does not sanitise and escape an invalid nonce before outputting it back in an AJAX response, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
